Interface VPrincipalEventos

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.WindowListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccionEventoVPrincipal
    public interface VPrincipalEventos
extends java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.WindowListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener
    Interfaz hija de ActionListener, WindowListener y MouseListener que gestiona los eventos de la vista Main
